6.Write a query to display the courier details such as COURIER_ID, 
  FROM_ADDRESS, TO_ADDRESS and the STATUS of the couriers Delivered
  in the month of JANUARY

ans:

sort the records based on to_address in ascending order[acenture interview question]


SQL> SELECT * FROM COURIER;

    COURIER_ID     FROM_ADDRESS        TO_ADDRESS     EXPECTED_DELIVERY_DATE
   -----------    ---------------     -----------    ------------------------
       101	   Chennai	        Mumbai	         2025-01-15
       102	   Delhi	        Bangalore	 2025-01-20
       103	   Hyderabad	        Pune	         2025-02-25
       104	   Kolkata	        Ahmedabad	 2025-01-05
       105	   Mumbai	        Delhi	         2025-03-10


SQL> SELECT * FROM COURIER_STATUS;

    COURIER_ID       STATUS      ACTUAL_DELIVERED_DATE
    ---------      ----------    --------------------
      101	   Delivered	   2025-01-16
      102	   In Transit	     
      103	   Delivered	   2025-02-26
      104	   Delivered	   2025-01-06
      105	   Delivered	   2025-03-11


ans:
   select c.COURIER_ID,c.FROM_ADDRESS,c.TO_ADDRESS,cs.STATUS from COURIER as c
full join COURIER_STATUS as cs on  c.COURIER_ID=cs.COURIER_ID

